pesticide.PPE: Coveralls; Chemical-resistant gloves such as nitrile or butyl; Shoes plus socks; Protective eyewear

Safety_Information.general_Info: CAUTION: Harmful if swallowed, inhaled, or absorbed through skin. Avoid contact with eyes, skin, or clothing. Avoid breathing mists or vapors. This product may cause skin sensitization reactions in some people.
Safety_Information.if_Swallowed: Call a poison control center or doctor immediately for treatment advice. Have person sip a glass of water if able to swallow. Do not induce vomiting unless told to by a poison control center or doctor. Do not give anything to an unconscious person.
Safety_Information.if_On_Skin: Take off contaminated clothing. Rinse skin immediately with plenty of water for 15 – 20 minutes. Call a poison control center or doctor for treatment advice.
Safety_Information.physician_Note: For 24 hour medical emergency assistance (human or animal), or chemical emergency assistance (spill, leak, fire, or accident). Call CHEMTREC at 1-800-424-9300.
